column5: this ones for you T.J.  just so you know your advertising does get seen by some!  Matt!
care to share where this ad is?

That board is a landmark for me. It is on the North side of westbound HWY #17 just west of Sturgeon Falls.  ps. It's also on the north side if you're eastbound but you'll get a crick in your neck if you try to see it from that angle.
Me too Roy, once I pass that spot I know I'm only 30 minutes away  Won't be long now

It looks in much better repair then the last time I saw it! Seeing that sign lets me know that I am in the Near North.... ohhh and for some reason it reminds me of a large dude eating steaks off a plate..
The New Sign is much better LOL We Saw the sign!!!
